# Leacme.Voice Choice

**Leacme Voice Choice** is a cross-platform application that is currently targeted for mobile devices. It is build using the [Godot Engine](https://github.com/godotengine/godot).

This application features the ability to modulate and play back the audio input from your microphone.

![][image_screenshot]

## Application Compiling

The application can be compiled into the platform-specific executable with the Godot Engine via the following [instructions](https://docs.godotengine.org/en/latest/getting_started/workflow/export/index.html). Make sure to run `nuget restore` to fetch dependencies specified in the .csproj file prior to building with Godot.

## Application Usage

Enable the desired options by toggling buttons in the audio effects chain and speak into the device's microphone.
